Source: sphinx-ditaa
Maintainer: Jean-Jacques Brucker <jean-jacques.brucker@supersonicimagine.com>
Section: python
Priority: optional
Build-Depends: python-all (>= 2.6.6-3~), debhelper (>= 9~), dh-python,
               python-setuptools, python3-all, python3-setuptools 
Standards-Version: 3.9.1
X-Python-Version: >= 2.6
X-Python3-Version: >= 3.2

Package: python-sphinx-ditaa
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, ditaa, python-sphinx
Description: This adds a basic ditaa builder for sphinx.
 Sphinx is a documentation generator.
 Ditaa is a command-line utility, that can convert diagrams drawn using ascii
 art, into proper bitmap graphics. 

Package: python3-sphinx-ditaa
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, ditaa, python3-sphinx
Description: This adds a basic ditaa builder for sphinx.
 Sphinx is a documentation generator.
 Ditaa is a command-line utility, that can convert diagrams drawn using ascii
 art, into proper bitmap graphics. 
